Resistance.help: Demonlings are resistant to Placate and Disorient effects. They are also resistant to Lethal, Smashing, Fire, Cold and Toxic damage. They can also use Corruption on their foes.
Resistance.shortHelp: Auto Res Placate, Disorient, Terrorize, Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Toxic
Resistance.targetHelp: Demonlings are resistant to Placate and Disorient effects. They are also resistant to Lethal, Smashing, Fire, Cold and Toxic damage. They can also use Corruption on their foes.
Resistance.targetShortHelp: Auto Res Placate, Disorient, Terrorize, Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Toxic

Corruption.help: You fire a bolt of hellfire corrupting your victim's very living essence dealing minor toxic damage as well as reducing their damage resistance for a short time. Damage: Minor Recharge: Very Fast
Corruption.shortHelp: Ranged, Minor DMG(Fire), Foe Minor DoT (Toxic), -Res
Corruption.targetHelp: Corruption continues to deal additional toxic damage over time as well as reducing your target's damage resistance.
